rc=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"425671f855fe7dbabf91d00cb3c36b7e3ced66ce","tid":323763,"uid":62079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T05:29:28.000Z","msg":"巴打租車幾錢？點計？<br />\n自駕遊大陸洗唔洗好小心，成日覺得大陸人揸車好亂黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da1028792d284389d3dbe964d12680938ca0e85d","tid":323763,"uid":81113,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T05:33:32.000Z","msg":"無米粥？膠水就膠水啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09de3175a057503ca5ae62b34a410ed02f02d35a","tid":323763,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T05:46:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打租車幾錢？點計？<br />\n自駕遊大陸洗唔洗好小心，成日覺得大陸人揸車好亂黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n請睇上面回覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb5830658d54473fe191bf114b559e44a93a573c","tid":323763,"uid":49791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T06:08:37.000Z","msg":"其實大陸揸係幾危險<br />\n佢地永遠轉線唔打燈唔望盲點<br />\n覺得成條路得自己<br />\n佢突然cut 線要自己剎停<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好多人都係因為政府收地<br />\n搞到好有錢 就去買車<br />\n但其實本身就冇乜技術<br />\n民智未開<br />\n夠膽死為左影彩虹 停左係條freeway 既中線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n道路設計and 環境好差<br />\n上年行山路轉灣位突然條路有油<br />\n差d 跣撚左出去海邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n電動單車好撚多<br />\n佢地唔識道路規則<br />\n總之係意外頻生<br />\n<br />\n係大陸揸車唔算難<br />\n但一定要好撚小心<br />\n因為大陸狗真係太撚多on9<br />\n一唔小心會累死你"},{"pid":"2c2caa7565a3b31e0c922e263d8f6175a0a1132f","tid":323763,"uid":38425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T06:10:14.000Z","msg":"又係巴打你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  上次架別克同呢次係咪差好遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bbbcdb19a3a020299dd17ef47262466d0445fb6","tid":323763,"uid":79410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T06:15:33.000Z","msg":"拎左個大陸牌都係楂過一次.<br />\n個次楂左去連州.<br />\n好想楂去海南. 但係又冇朋友陪&amp;有興趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25242dccf68db8f0ca4065979176c117d0d241bc","tid":323763,"uid":32527,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T06:16:38.000Z","msg":"咁撚愛國咪撚返黎香港啦<br />\n支那豬"},{"pid":"6ea4352785148bac8297bb0d310e750d574ed6e1","tid":323763,"uid":45895,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T06:25:26.000Z","msg":"咁多地方唔去，點解要去鬼國呢？"},{"pid":"5893f2da16d215f3e30ce4623f6a1ae4088babab","tid":323763,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T06:53:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又係巴打你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  上次架別克同呢次係咪差好遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n別克好好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我租過雪鐵龍愛麗舍同宜家呢次租標緻<br />\n我覺得呢d法國車操控麻麻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6a804bf3c2f25d824b127983e8b3a7d3c4d20c1","tid":323763,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T06:54:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>拎左個大陸牌都係楂過一次.<br />\n個次楂左去連州.<br />\n好想楂去海南. 但係又冇朋友陪&amp;有興趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n海南有冇得坐汽車渡輪"},{"pid":"8962e78fd56833fb67dc8f80ce5ee6963dc047b7","tid":323763,"uid":14378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"ci